## Stack
- React 19, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind v4
- Tokens in tokens.css inside @theme {} — NO tailwind.config.ts
- Icons: @phosphor-icons/react
- Typeface: Space Grotesk

## Critical rules
- NEVER hardcode hex, px, font names, or border-radius in components.
  Always use CSS custom properties from tokens.css.
- ALWAYS update /styleguide when adding a new component or visual pattern.
- No new tokens without role-based naming (e.g. --color-bg-editor-canvas).
- Reuse existing components: StatusPill, Divider, NavItem, AccountRow.

## Architecture
- Editor route is INSIDE AppShell (same as Library, Device, Explore).
- Editor left panel is in Sidebar.tsx — renders when route is /editor.
- Editor.tsx contains only: FanCanvas (center) + ZoneSettings (right panel).
- Fan canvas uses HTML Canvas (not SVG).
- Fan geometry math lives in src/utils/fanGeometry.ts.

## Editor rules
- Zone color ≠ LED color. Zone color = canvas visual only.
- LED color = preset gradient (colorA + colorB) → device LED.
- No MIDI Learn — removed from MVP scope.
- Scale is preset-level, not per-zone.
- Editor is always free-form — no Standard/Experimental mode toggle.
